#: ../../source/language/php/stream.rst:88
msgid "XXE读取文件时会因而解析报错，可用base64编码"
msgstr "When XXE reads files, parsing errors may occur, so base64 encoding can be used."

#: ../../source/language/php/stream.rst:89
msgid "base64编码会弃掉未在码表内的字符，可用于绕过一些文件格式"
msgstr "Base64 encoding discards characters that are not in the alphabet, which can be used to bypass some file formats."

#: ../../source/language/php/stream.rst:90
msgid "部分 convert 会有大量的资源消耗，可用作DoS"
msgstr "Some convert filters consume many resources and can be used for DoS."

#: ../../source/language/php/stream.rst:91
msgid "rot13 / convert 转换 过WAF"
msgstr "rot13 / convert transformations can bypass WAFs."
